name: GeneratedNews
0:
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Stay informed (or at least entertained) with Generated News, your go-to flash briefing for a mix of real headlines and satirical stories. Whether you’re looking for breaking news or a good laugh, Generated News has you covered with quirky takes on current events, unexpected twists, and just the right amount of humor. Perfect for anyone who wants to stay in the know while keeping things lighthearted. Tune in daily for updates that blur the line between news and satire! 

You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
